    "# Trading Behavioral Anomaly Detection"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "dc49e9b4-1076-4289-a7ea-f18cc01c6623",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Problem Statement:\n",
    "Detect unusual trading behavior patterns from historical execution data using unsupervised learning.\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Potential use cases:\n",
    "\n",
    "- suspicious activity monitoring\n",
    "- bot / abnormal behavior detection\n",
    "- risk monitoring\n",
    "- user segmentation support"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a0128b8a-c6fe-4e82-84f6-cccf1d37469f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Dataset Overview:\n",
    "#### Summary:\n",
    "- 211,224 transaction rows\n",
    "- 16 columns\n",
    "- each row = one executed trade\n",
    "- user-level identifier (Primary Entity) is \"Account\"\n",
    "#### Important columns:\n",
    "- Account\n",
    "- Timestamp\n",
    "- Size USD\n",
    "- Coin\n",
    "- Side\n",
    "- Direction\n",
    "- Closed PnL"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "e0322a80-4f1c-483f-88c1-f4c80b140e55",
