   "source": [
    "#### Entity Mapping:\n",
    "    - User ID: Account\n",
    "    - Asset: Coin\n",
    "    - Timestamp: Timestamp / Timestamp IST\n",
    "    - Action: Side, Direction\n",
    "    - Trade size: Size USD, Size Tokens\n",
    "    - Outcome: Closed PnL\n",
    "    - Market context: Execution Price\n",
    "    - Transaction metadata: Order ID, Trade ID, Transaction Hash"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "62c20b0a-8e3f-4f3a-a9c2-c02a80adb0ca",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Key Challenge:\n",
    "- No labels available.\n",
    "\n",
    "#### So:\n",
    "- cannot use supervised fraud classification\n",
    "- must detect unusual behavior patterns statistically\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Therefore:\n",
    "- Unsupervised anomaly detection"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5d9478b6-7ac7-4727-9fa8-6ba17306ee10",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Behavioral Feature Engineering\n",
    "- Transform raw trades into user-day behavior."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8ac7bf98-aba7-4054-8ba8-509ed4bbfc2b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Behavioral Features Definition\n",
    "\n",
    "We define the following user-level behavioral features for anomaly detection:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. trades_per_day\n",
    "2. total_trade_volume_per_day\n",
    "3. avg_trade_size\n",
    "4. time_between_trades (optional / derived)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3605e821-1d9e-4d64-aed4-b923b6dc4f7f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Feature Feasibility Check\n",
    "\n",
    "We validate whether the dataset supports computation of the defined behavioral features."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b296932d-58aa-4685-9712-de4dfaf8dafa",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "All 4 core behavioral features are directly available from transaction-level fields in the dataset without extra assumptions.\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Feature <-> Column Mapping\n",
    "\n",
    "    - trades_per_day -> Account + Timestamp\n",
    "    - total_trades_volume_per_day -> Size USD + Account + Timestamp\n",
    "    - avg_trading_size -> Size USD aggregated per Account/Day\n",
    "    - time_between_trades -> Timestamp deltas per Account"
   ]
  },
