    "## 7. Explainability Layer\n",
    "### 7.1 Explainability Objective\n",
    "- For each detected anomaly, we identify which behavioral features contributed most to its abnormality.\n",
    "- This is done by comparing each feature value to the global population distribution."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
