   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 7.2 Feature Baseline Statistics\n",
    "- We compute global statistics (median and standard deviation) for each feature to define \"normal behavior\"."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 45,
   "id": "236e59ec-6a3c-46a1-bf66-530ba55f3f55",
