    "## 8. Limitations\n",
    "### 8.1 Core Limitations of the Current Approach\n",
    "- This anomaly detection system is based on unsupervised learning and behavioral aggregation.\n",
    "- As a result, it has several inherent limitations that must be acknowledged for production use."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d74569fd-45b2-4daf-9a49-62fc43e2f9e2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 8.2 Population-Level vs User-Level Behavior\n",
    "- The model learns a global behavioral baseline across all accounts.\n",
    "\n",
    "#### This introduces a key limitation:\n",
    "- A \"high-volume trader\" may appear normal globally\n",
    "- but could still be abnormal relative to their own historical behavior"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "859d63e3-4b2e-48c2-824c-f0e09677dc1c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 8.3 No Ground Truth Labels\n",
    "- There are no labeled fraud or anomaly indicators in the dataset.\n",
    "#### Implications:\n",
    "- Cannot compute precision / recall / F1\n",
    "- Cannot validate true fraud detection performance\n",
    "- Evaluation is based only on behavioral plausibility"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "6bc0a14b-c42d-43f5-89b2-34252502ec5d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 8.4 Missing Financial and Market Context\n",
    "#### The current feature set does not include:\n",
    "- leverage usage\n",
    "- margin exposure\n",
    "- market volatility at trade time\n",
    "- portfolio-level PnL trajectory\n",
    "- risk-adjusted exposure metrics\n",
    "#### This limits the ability to distinguish:\n",
    "- aggressive trading vs normal strategy behavior\n",
    "- informed trading vs random activity"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1048ba7f-3b7a-4e19-bcb2-edae913e3d64",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 8.5 Temporal Aggregation Loss\n",
    "- The model operates at a user-day aggregation level.\n",
    "#### This causes:\n",
    "- loss of intra-day structure\n",
    "- inability to detect micro-bursts within a day\n",
    "- reduced sensitivity to short-term manipulation patterns"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "316e3bbe-fa00-4cbd-823e-35eb054413d9",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 8.6 Fixed Anomaly Proportion Assumption\n",
    "- Isolation Forest assumes a fixed contamination rate (e.g., 1%).\n",
    "#### This introduces:\n",
    "- dependency on manual tuning\n",
    "- no adaptive anomaly thresholding\n",
    "- potential mismatch with real-world anomaly frequency"
   ]
  },
